🔥 Production Scenario
Problem

A Jenkins server fails because /var is full.

Investigation

Check filesystem usage:

df -h

Find large directories:

du -sh /var/* | sort -hr

Find large log files:

find /var/log -type f -size +100M

Check deleted-but-open files:

sudo lsof +L1

Archive or rotate old logs, then verify free space:

df -h
